  <div class="ten columns additional_info centered clearfix">

    <div class="eleven columns centered donation_box">
      <h3>Go Pro!</h3>
      <p class="sub_text">Looking to import your LinkedIn profile? Want to keep track of the hits on your resume? <br />Check out the PRO version, We are sure that you'll love it.</p>
      <ul class="row">
        <li class="four columns">
          <h4>Complete analytics</h4>
